The event on everyone’s lips and Nigeria’s first Bridal Fashion Week is a few weeks away. Find out all you need to know about the ultimate bridal experience happening in Lagos from the 4th to the 6th of May, 2018. Lagos Bridal Fashion Week is a three-day experience that will feature a curated list of Pan-African bridal designers for the daily runway shows and brands at the BFW Bridal Boutique. The boutique will house a collection of vendors retailing bridal (and wedding) items as well as private rooms for consultations with designers and bridal stylists. From the 4th to the 6th of May, 2018 at the Balmoral Convention Centre, Federal Palace, Victoria Island. Brides -to-be, Groom-to-be, Parents, Bridal Fashion Enthusiasts, Bridal Stylists, Aspiring Brides & Grooms, Friends of soon to be couples etc… 1. Daily Installations by: 2. Runway shows featuring designers from Africa, UK and USA. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-614605 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1000" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule.jpg 1024w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule-598x598.jpg 598w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule-100x100.jpg 100w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule-200x200.jpg 200w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule-487x487.jpg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule-974x974.jpg 974w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule-240x240.jpg 240w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule-480x480.jpg 480w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-Day1-Schedule-600x600.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-614607 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/LBFW-RunwaySchedule-Day-2-423x598.jpg" alt="" w